thread.title: BRIEF-Qingdao Tianhua Institute Chemistry Engineering to swing to loss in FY 2017

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Qingdao Tianhua Institute Chemistry Engineering to swing to loss in FY 2017

organizations.name: qingdao tianhua institute chemistry engineering co ltd

text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Qingdao Tianhua Institute Chemistry Engineering Co Ltd :
* Sees to swing to net loss at 40 million yuan to 48 million yuan in FY 2017 versus net profit at 6.3 million yuan year ago
* Says decreased sale price and increased raw material price as main reasons for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/5oiJYf
